Well, then go get him, for heaven's sake!

720
00:45:11,570 --> 00:45:13,400
要是我们遇到印第安人怎么办?
What if we run into the Indians?

721
00:45:13,440 --> 00:45:16,240
那就用枪来对付他们
That's what guns are for.

722
00:45:16,280 --> 00:45:18,570
马上武装起来出发!
Now arm yourselves and get moving!

723
00:45:44,000 --> 00:45:45,970
Pocahontas啊
Pocahontas.

724
00:45:46,010 --> 00:45:48,940
你应该待在部落里
You should be inside the village.

725
00:45:48,980 --> 00:45:50,530
我们会没事的
We'll be all right.

726
00:45:50,580 --> 00:45:53,770
我们正在为战士们准备食物
We're gathering food for when the warriors arrive.

727
00:45:53,810 --> 00:45:54,970
不要走太远了
Don't go far.

728
00:45:55,010 --> 00:45:56,740
现在不是到处乱跑的时候
Now is not the time to be running off.

729
00:45:56,780 --> 00:45:58,410
是的 父亲
Yes, Father.

730
00:45:59,890 --> 00:46:02,320
当我看到你戴着那串项链...
When I see you wear that necklace...

731
00:46:02,360 --> 00:46:05,050
你就像你母亲一样
you look just like your mother.

732
00:46:05,090 --> 00:46:06,650
我想她
I miss her.

733
00:46:06,690 --> 00:46:09,060
但她仍然和我们在一起
But she is still with us.

734
00:46:09,100 --> 00:46:11,560
无论何时风吹过树林...
Whenever the wind moves through the trees...

735
00:46:11,600 --> 00:46:13,330
我就感觉到她的存在
I feel her presence.

736
00:46:13,370 --> 00:46:16,300
我们的人民向她祈祷智慧和力量
Our people looked to her for wisdom and strength.

737
00:46:16,340 --> 00:46:19,070
有一天 他们也会向你祈祷
Someday, they will look to you as well.

738
00:46:19,110 --> 00:46:21,940
我会感到无限荣耀
I would be honoured by that.

739
00:46:21,980 --> 00:46:23,740
你不应该单独待在这儿
You shouldn't be out here alone.

740
00:46:23,780 --> 00:46:25,940
我会叫Kocoum过来的
I'll send for Kocoum.

741
00:46:25,980 --> 00:46:27,470
好了 到底怎么回事?
All right. What is it?

742
00:46:27,510 --> 00:46:28,980
- 什么? - 你隐瞒着什么东西
- What? - You're hiding something.

743
00:46:29,020 --> 00:46:30,950
我没有隐瞒任何东西
I'm not hiding anything.

744
00:46:30,980 --> 00:46:33,150
Pocahontas 你可以告诉我 我发誓
Pocahontas, you can tell me. I promise

745
00:46:33,190 --> 00:46:37,180
我不会告诉任何人的... Pocahontas 看!
I won't tell anyone... Pocahontas, look!

746
00:46:40,630 --> 00:46:42,090
这是他们其中一个! 我要去找...
It's one of them! I'm going to get...

747
00:46:42,130 --> 00:46:44,320
你在这儿干什么?
What are you doing here?

748
00:46:44,360 --> 00:46:46,360
我必须要再见你一次
I had to see you again.

749
00:46:46,400 --> 00:46:48,090
Pocahontas啊!
Pocahontas!

750
00:46:48,130 --> 00:46:49,600
Pocahontas啊!
Pocahontas!

751
00:46:49,640 --> 00:46:51,470
求你! 不要说任何事
Please! Don't say anything.

752
00:46:51,500 --> 00:46:53,130
快! 这边!
Quick! this way!

753
00:46:53,170 --> 00:46:54,700
- 但是... - Nakoma
- But... - Nakoma.

754
00:46:54,740 --> 00:46:56,440
Pocahontas呢?
Where is Pocahontas?

755
00:46:56,480 --> 00:46:59,270
我... 我没有看到她
I... I haven't seen her.

756
00:46:59,310 --> 00:47:02,440
Pocahontas不能再到处乱跑了
Pocahontas can't keep running off.

757
00:47:02,480 --> 00:47:04,310
外面很危险
It's dangerous out there.

758
00:47:04,350 --> 00:47:07,750
告诉她这些 她听你的话
Tell her that. She listens to you.

759
00:47:09,090 --> 00:47:11,890
嗨! 她当然听我的
Huh! Sure she does.

760
00:47:27,310 --> 00:47:30,040
这个地方实在太难以置信了
This place is incredible.

761
00:47:30,080 --> 00:47:31,340
想想我们长途跋涉...
And to think we came all this way...

762
00:47:31,380 --> 00:47:32,640
只是为了挖金子
just to dig it up for gold.

763
00:47:32,680 --> 00:47:34,170
金子?
Gold?

764
00:47:34,210 --> 00:47:36,880
- 嗨 Meeko - 什么是金子?
- Hey, Meeko. - What's gold?

765
00:47:36,920 --> 00:47:38,980
你也许知道 就是... 黄黄的
You know, it's, uh... it's, it's yellow.

766
00:47:39,020 --> 00:47:41,380
从地里头挖出来的 非常宝贵
It comes out of the ground. It's really valuable.

767
00:47:41,420 --> 00:47:43,360
哦! 这个 我们这儿有很多
Oh! Here, we have lots of it.

768
00:47:43,390 --> 00:47:45,720
金子
Gold.

769
00:47:45,760 --> 00:47:49,560
不 不! 金子是这个
No No! Gold is this.

770
00:47:49,600 --> 00:47:52,220
这附近没有这样的东西
There's nothing like that around here.

771
00:47:52,270 --> 00:47:54,890
- 没有金子? - 至少我没见过
- No gold? - Not that I've seen.

772
00:47:54,930 --> 00:47:57,730
这一趟算是白跑了
All this way for nothing.

773
00:47:57,770 --> 00:48:00,570
那些孩子们将会大吃一惊的
Well, those boys are in for a big surprise.

774
00:48:00,610 --> 00:48:03,010
- 他们会离开吗? - 其中一些可能会
- Will they leave? - Some of them might.

775
00:48:05,210 --> 00:48:06,510
你会回家吗?
Will you go home?

776
00:48:06,550 --> 00:48:10,070
我没什么家可回的
Well, it's not like I have much of a home to go back to.

777
00:48:10,120 --> 00:48:12,520
我从来没有 真正属于过任何地方
I've never really belonged anywhere.

778
00:48:12,550 --> 00:48:15,350
你可以属于这儿
You could belong here.

779
00:48:23,500 --> 00:48:25,430
那是什么?!
What was that?!

780
00:48:25,470 --> 00:48:26,930
你看到什么了吗?
Did you see something?

781
00:48:26,970 --> 00:48:29,870
不 不 我只是...我...
No. No. I just, uh... I...

782
00:48:29,900 --> 00:48:33,170
我没有看到任何东西 是不是?
I didn't see anything, did I?

783
00:48:33,210 --> 00:48:34,700
再看一次
Look again.

784
00:48:35,980 --> 00:48:38,710
# 让它来指引你 #
# Let it break upon you #

785
00:48:38,750 --> 00:48:44,380
# 就像波浪打在沙滩上 #
# Like a wave upon the sand #

786
00:48:44,420 --> 00:48:47,390
你好 John Smith
Hello, John Smith.

787
00:48:47,420 --> 00:48:50,320
Pocahontas 那棵树在和我说话
Pocahontas, that tree is talking to me.

788
00:48:50,360 --> 00:48:52,590
那么你就应该回答
Then you should talk back.

789
00:48:52,630 --> 00:48:54,560
不要害怕 年轻人
Don't be frightened, young man.

790
00:48:54,590 --> 00:48:57,500
我的树皮比我咬的更痛
My bark is worse than my bite.

791
00:48:58,870 --> 00:49:00,590
说点什么
Say something.

792
00:49:00,630 --> 00:49:02,620
对一棵树应该说些什么?
What do you say to a tree?

793
00:49:02,670 --> 00:49:04,660
任何你想说的
Anything you want.

794
00:49:08,240 --> 00:49:09,540
那么 恩...
So, uh...

795
00:49:09,580 --> 00:49:13,170
靠近些 John Smith
Come closer, John Smith.

796
00:49:13,210 --> 00:49:15,810
他有一个善良的灵魂
He has a good soul.

797
00:49:15,850 --> 00:49:17,610
他也很帅气!
And he's handsome too!

798
00:49:17,650 --> 00:49:21,050
- 哦 我喜欢她 - 我知道你会的
- Oh, I like her. - I knew you would.

799
00:49:21,090 --> 00:49:22,320
Smith啊!
Smith!

800
00:49:22,360 --> 00:49:24,620
Smith 你在哪儿 伙计?
Smith Where are you, mate?

801
00:49:24,660 --> 00:49:25,850
我们不能让他们看见
We can't let them see us.

802
00:49:25,890 --> 00:49:27,330
快! 到这儿来
Quick! Over here.

803
00:49:27,360 --> 00:49:29,120
这个地方让我害怕
This place gives me the creeps.

804
00:49:29,160 --> 00:49:31,220
野蛮人可能躲在任何地方
Savages could be hiding anywhere.

805
00:49:31,260 --> 00:49:36,200
对 如果你发现一个 不要多想 尽管开枪就是
Aye. Well, if you spot one, don't ask questions. Just shoot.

806
00:49:37,540 --> 00:49:39,370
小心你的脚 你个畸形儿!
Watch your feet, you big oaf!

807
00:49:39,410 --> 00:49:41,200
不是我 是这棵树
It wasn't me. It was the tree.

808
00:49:41,240 --> 00:49:42,400
哦 当然!
Oh, of course!

809
00:49:42,440 --> 00:49:44,880
这棵树好像把它的根抬了一下...
The tree just felt like lifting its roots and...

810
00:49:48,250 --> 00:49:49,650
我们赶快离开这儿
Let's get out of here.

811
00:49:51,180 --> 00:49:52,810
- 啊哦! 快跑啊! - 啊哦!
- Ow! Run! - Ow!

812
00:49:52,850 --> 00:49:54,320
但是Smith怎么办?
But what about Smith?

813
00:49:54,350 --> 00:49:57,190
他已经是个大人了 他能够照顾自己的
He's a big lad. He can take care of himself.

814
00:49:57,220 --> 00:49:58,520
我真高兴你们能站在我这边
I'm glad you're on our side.

815
00:49:58,560 --> 00:50:01,620
这些古老的藤蔓 倒是还有些力气
There's still some snap in these old vines.

816
00:50:01,660 --> 00:50:04,390
我最好在他们把所有人 都派来找我之前赶回去
I'd better get back before they send the whole camp out after me.

817
00:50:04,430 --> 00:50:06,130
我们什么时候能再见面?
When will I see you again?

818
00:50:06,170 --> 00:50:08,430
今天晚上 就在这儿
Meet me tonight. Right here.

819
00:50:13,510 --> 00:50:18,310
嗯 我已经200年 没有碰到这种兴奋的事了
Well, I haven't had this much excitement in 200 years.

820
00:50:18,340 --> 00:50:21,470
我到底在做什么? 我不应该再去见他了
What am I doing? I shouldn't be seeing him again.

821
00:50:21,510 --> 00:50:23,510
我的意思是 我还想再见到他
I mean, I want to see him again.

822
00:50:23,550 --> 00:50:26,640
谁不想? 我也想再见到他
Who wouldn't? I want to see him again.

823
00:50:26,690 --> 00:50:28,520
但是仍然 一种内在的感觉...
But still, something inside...

824
00:50:28,550 --> 00:50:30,650
在告诉我 这是对的
is telling me it's the right thing.

825
00:50:30,690 --> 00:50:32,390
或许这就是你的梦
Perhaps it's your dream.

826
00:50:32,430 --> 00:50:35,120
我的梦? 你是说他就是...
My dream? Do you think he's the one...

827
00:50:35,160 --> 00:50:37,530
那个旋转的箭头所指向的?
the spinning arrow was pointing to?

828
00:50:46,910 --> 00:50:48,430
战士们来了!
The warriors are here!

829
00:51:00,020 --> 00:51:03,150
Pocahontas 你疯了吗? 你到底在做什么?
Pocahontas, are you crazy? What were you doing with one of them?

830
00:51:03,190 --> 00:51:04,550
- 你在这儿! - Kocoum!
- There you are. - Kocoum!

831
00:51:04,590 --> 00:51:06,750
看看他们! 现在我们有足够的勇士...
Look at them! Now we have enough warriors...

832
00:51:06,790 --> 00:51:09,130
去摧毁那些白皮肤的魔鬼!
to destroy those white demons!

833
00:51:10,660 --> 00:51:12,890
既然我们的兄弟们加入了...
Now that we are joined by our brothers...

834
00:51:12,930 --> 00:51:14,990
我们就要去击败那些敌人
we will defeat this enemy.

835
00:51:22,440 --> 00:51:24,340
父亲 我想和你谈谈
Father, I need to speak with you.

836
00:51:24,380 --> 00:51:26,850
现在不行 我的女儿 首领们正在商量事情
Not now, my daughter. The council is gathering.

837
00:51:26,880 --> 00:51:30,410
我们并不需要和他们打仗 一定有一条更好的路可走
We don't have to fight them! There must be a better way.

838
00:51:30,450 --> 00:51:33,210
有时候我们的路是已经定了的
Sometimes our paths are chosen for us.

839
00:51:33,250 --> 00:51:35,780
但是也许我们 可以试着和他们谈谈
But maybe we should try talking to them.

840
00:51:35,820 --> 00:51:37,480
他们并不想谈判
They do not want to talk.

841
00:51:37,520 --> 00:51:39,550
但是如果他们 其中一个真的想要呢...
But if one of them did want to talk...

842
00:51:39,590 --> 00:51:41,320
你会听他的 是吗?
you would listen to him, wouldn't you?

843
00:51:41,360 --> 00:51:43,420
- Pocahontas - 是吗?
- Pocahontas. - Wouldn't you?

844
00:51:43,460 --> 00:51:47,760
我当然会 但是事情并不是那么简单
Of course I would. But it is not that simple.

845
00:51:47,800 --> 00:51:50,200
没有什么事情会这么简单的
Nothing is simple any more.

846
00:52:34,150 --> 00:52:37,450
别紧张 Thomas 是我
Easy, Thomas. It's me.

847
00:52:37,480 --> 00:52:40,280
哦 John 我差点打中你
Oh, John. I could've killed you.

848
00:52:40,320 --> 00:52:42,220
你这样瞄准是打不中我的
Not aiming like that, you couldn't.

849
00:52:42,260 --> 00:52:43,980
当你射击的时候 两只眼睛都睁着
Keep both eyes open when you shoot.

850
00:52:44,020 --> 00:52:45,920
你会瞄得准得多
You'll see twice as well.

851
00:52:45,960 --> 00:52:48,430
Smith 你回来了!
Smith, there you are!

852
00:52:48,460 --> 00:52:50,220
我们正四处找你
We were looking all over for you.

853
00:52:50,260 --> 00:52:53,490
Smith! 你刚刚去哪儿了?
Smith! Where have you been?

854
00:52:53,530 --> 00:52:56,300
我去观察地形了 长官
I was out scouting the terrain, sir.

855
00:52:56,340 --> 00:52:58,700
聪明 那么你一定 知道印第安人的行踪了
Excellent. Then you must know the Indians' whereabouts.

856
00:52:58,740 --> 00:53:00,330
这些信息对我们的 战役应该会有帮助的
We'll need that information for the battle.

857
00:53:00,370 --> 00:53:01,570
什么战役?
What battle?

858
00:53:01,610 --> 00:53:04,580
我们要把这些 野蛮人一次消灭干净
We will eliminate these savages once and for all.

859
00:53:04,610 --> 00:53:06,080
不! 你不能那么做!
No! You can't do that!

860
00:53:06,110 --> 00:53:08,980
哦 不能?
Oh, can't I?

861
00:53:09,020 --> 00:53:11,510
听着 我们并不需要和他们打仗
Look, we don't have to fight them.

862
00:53:11,550 --> 00:53:13,820
- John 你怎么了? - 我见过他们当中一个
- John, what's gotten into you? - I met one of them.

863
00:53:13,850 --> 00:53:16,340
- 你什么?! - 一个野蛮人?
- You what?! - A savage?

864
00:53:16,390 --> 00:53:19,050
他们不是野蛮人 他们能够帮助我们
They're not savages. They can help us.

865
00:53:19,090 --> 00:53:20,250
他们了解这片土地
They know the land.

866
00:53:20,290 --> 00:53:21,560
他们知道怎样在河里航行
They know how to navigate the rivers.

867
00:53:23,260 --> 00:53:25,360
- 再看 这是食物 - 这是什么?
- And look. It's food. - What is it?

868
00:53:25,400 --> 00:53:27,960
这个肯定比硬面饼和稀粥强
It's better than hardtack and gruel, that's for sure.

869
00:53:28,000 --> 00:53:29,190
我喜欢稀粥
I like gruel.

870
00:53:29,240 --> 00:53:31,640
他们不会给我们食物 你们这些笨蛋!
They don't want to feed us, you ninnies!

871
00:53:31,670 --> 00:53:34,470
他们想要杀死我们! 我们所有的人!
They want to kill us! All of us!

872
00:53:34,510 --> 00:53:35,740
他们拿走了我们的金子...
They've got our gold...

873
00:53:35,780 --> 00:53:37,500
为了留住它 他们会做出任何事情!
and they'll do anything to keep it!

874
00:53:37,540 --> 00:53:39,030
但是这儿没有金子
But there is no gold.

875
00:53:39,080 --> 00:53:41,050
没有金子?
No gold?

876
00:53:41,080 --> 00:53:45,410
我猜肯定是你的印第安小朋友告诉你的?
And I suppose your little Indian friend told you this?

877
00:53:45,450 --> 00:53:46,920
没错
Yes.

878
00:53:46,950 --> 00:53:50,550
谎言! 谎言! 一切都是谎言! 危险的小偷!
Lies! Lies! All of it! Murderous thieves!

879
00:53:50,590 --> 00:53:52,820
在文明世界中他们没有立足之地
There's no room for their kind in civilized society.

880
00:53:52,860 --> 00:53:54,290
但是这儿是他们的地盘!
But this is their land!

881
00:53:54,330 --> 00:53:57,730
这是我的地盘! 我在这儿制定法律
This is my land! I make the laws here.

882
00:53:57,760 --> 00:54:02,060
我说过任何人一旦发现了印第安人...
And I say anyone who so much as looks at an Indian...

883
00:54:02,100 --> 00:54:03,660
而没有将他当场杀死的...
without killing him on sight...

884
00:54:03,700 --> 00:54:07,900
将被判为叛国罪而处以绞刑!
will be tried for treason and hanged!

885
00:54:12,590 --> 00:54:13,890
Pocahontas啊!
Pocahontas!

886
00:54:13,920 --> 00:54:15,860
- Nakoma! - 不要出去
- Nakoma! - Don't go out there.

887
00:54:15,890 --> 00:54:19,220
我为你撒过一次谎 不要让我再做一次
I lied for you once. Don't ask me to do it again.

888
00:54:19,260 --> 00:54:20,730
我必须要这样做
I have to do this.

889
00:54:20,760 --> 00:54:22,960
- 他是他们其中之一! - 你不了解他
- He's one of them! - You don't know him.

890
00:54:23,000 --> 00:54:24,160
如果你去了那儿...
If you go out there...

891
00:54:24,200 --> 00:54:26,030
你就背叛了你自己的族人
You'll be turning your back on your own people.

892
00:54:26,070 --> 00:54:28,470
我在努力拯救我的族人
I'm trying to help my people.

893
00:54:28,500 --> 00:54:32,030
Pocahontas 求你 你是我最好的朋友
Pocahontas, please. You're my best friend.

894
00:54:32,070 --> 00:54:33,600
我不想看到你受到伤害
I don't want you to get hurt.

895
00:54:33,640 --> 00:54:35,610
我不会的 我知道我自己在做什么
I won't. I know what I'm doing.

896
00:54:35,640 --> 00:54:38,200
Pocahontas 不!
Pocahontas, no!

897
00:54:43,720 --> 00:54:45,080
Ratcliffe不会让我们...
Ratcliffe wouldn't take us...

898
00:54:45,120 --> 00:54:46,850
在这个世界什么都找不到
halfway around the world for nothin'.

899
00:54:46,890 --> 00:54:48,650
但是如果Smith说得是真的呢?
But what if Smith is right?

900
00:54:48,690 --> 00:54:50,590
如果真的没有金子该怎么办?
What if there is no gold?

901
00:54:50,630 --> 00:54:51,890
如果你问我...
If you ask me...

902
00:54:51,930 --> 00:54:53,790
Ratcliffe从我们离开伦敦的时候就在骗我们
Ratcliffe's been lying to us since we left London.

903
00:54:53,830 --> 00:54:55,760
听着 你们这些白痴
Listen to you, ya bunch of idiots.

904
00:54:55,800 --> 00:54:58,130
那些野蛮人不会吃了没事和我们打战的
Those savages didn't attack us for nothin'.

905
00:54:58,170 --> 00:55:00,030
他们一定在隐藏着什么东西
They're hidin' somethin'.

906
00:55:00,070 --> 00:55:01,700
如果他们真的有金子...
If they do have the gold...

907
00:55:01,740 --> 00:55:03,530
我想我们会和他们打战的
I reckon we'll have to fight 'em.

908
00:55:03,570 --> 00:55:06,200
要不太冷要不太热
Either too hot or too cool.

909
00:55:06,240 --> 00:55:09,510
我从一到这儿就没舒服过
I haven't been comfortable since we got here.

910
00:55:09,550 --> 00:55:13,350
哦 我也是 我痒得难受
Oh, I know. I've been itching a lot.

911
00:55:19,490 --> 00:55:22,010
- 跟着他 - 是的 长官
- Follow him. - Yes, Governor.

912
00:55:22,060 --> 00:55:23,990
我想知道他偷偷地跑去哪儿
I want to know where he's sneaking off to.

913
00:55:24,030 --> 00:55:25,190
是的 长官
Yes, sir.

914
00:55:25,230 --> 00:55:28,460
如果你遇到什么印第安人
And if you happen to see any Indians,

915
00:55:28,500 --> 00:55:30,090
开枪打死他
Shoot them.

916
00:55:33,870 --> 00:55:36,600
哦 Thomas 你已经是一个差劲的水手
Oh, and Thomas, you've been a slipshod sailor

917
00:55:36,640 --> 00:55:39,270
又是一个可怜的士兵
and a poor excuse for a soldier.

918
00:55:39,310 --> 00:55:41,470
不要让我再次失望
Don't disappoint me again.

919
00:55:51,090 --> 00:55:53,650
- Kocoum - 什么事?
- Kocoum. - What is it?

920
00:55:53,690 --> 00:55:55,780
是关于Pocahontas的
It's Pocahontas.

921
00:55:55,820 --> 00:55:58,550
怎么了? 她还好吗?
What's wrong? Is she all right?

922
00:56:00,600 --> 00:56:02,590
我想她有麻烦了
I think she's in trouble.

923
00:56:07,040 --> 00:56:10,130
大地在颤抖 孩子 发生什么事了?
The Earth is trembling, child. What's happened?

924
00:56:10,170 --> 00:56:11,610
战士们在这儿!
The warriors are here!

925
00:56:11,640 --> 00:56:14,770
- Pocahontas啊! - John啊!
- Pocahontas! - John!

926
00:56:14,810 --> 00:56:16,240
听我说
Listen to me.

927
00:56:16,280 --> 00:56:18,640
我们的人正在计划攻击你的族人
My men are planning to attack your people.

928
00:56:18,680 --> 00:56:19,840
你得去通知他们
You've got to warn them.

929
00:56:19,880 --> 00:56:22,350
也许现在阻止这些还不算太晚
Maybe it's not too late to stop this.

930
00:56:22,380 --> 00:56:24,320
你得跟我一起回去 去和我父亲谈判
You have to come with me and talk to my father.

931
00:56:24,350 --> 00:56:27,080
Pocahontas 谈判已经没有用了
Pocahontas, talking isn't going to do any good.

932
00:56:27,120 --> 00:56:28,920
我已经努力地去和我们的人谈了...
I already tried talking to my men...

933
00:56:28,960 --> 00:56:31,050
但是这片土地上的任何一件事情都让他们感到恐惧
but everything about this land has them spooked.

934
00:56:35,730 --> 00:56:38,200
那是我见过的最奇怪的生物!
That's the strangest creature I've ever seen.

935
00:56:42,240 --> 00:56:43,860
Percy啊?!
Percy?!

936
00:56:45,340 --> 00:56:47,810
放松点 Percy! 到这儿来!
Easy, Percy! Come here!

937
00:56:47,840 --> 00:56:49,040
Meeko 回来!
Meeko, come back!

938
00:56:49,080 --> 00:56:50,540
你看这就是我的意思?
You see what I mean?

939
00:56:50,580 --> 00:56:51,880
一旦双方准备开仗 谁也挡不住
Once two sides want to fight, nothing can stop them.

940
00:56:51,910 --> 00:56:53,310
过来 你们俩都给我过来!
Come Come here, both of you!

941
00:56:53,350 --> 00:56:55,210
好了! 好了! 他是一个朋友!
It's all right! It's all right! He's a friend!

942
00:56:55,250 --> 00:56:56,550
坏! 坏狗! 坐下!
Bad! Bad dog! Sit!

943
00:56:58,820 --> 00:57:01,650
- 你在干什么? Meeko! - Pency 回到这里来!
- What are you doing? Meeko! - Percy, get back here!

944
00:57:01,690 --> 00:57:02,990
你在干什么? 停下来!
What are you doing? Stop that!

945
00:57:03,030 --> 00:57:05,520
好了 够了!
All right, that's enough!

946
00:57:12,500 --> 00:57:14,830
足够让你的体液沸腾
It's enough to make your sap boil.

947
00:57:16,510 --> 00:57:20,970
现在 我有东西给你们看 看!
Now then, there's something I want to show you. Look.

948
00:57:24,750 --> 00:57:25,970
波纹
The ripples.

949
00:57:26,980 --> 00:57:28,210
他们什么意思?
What about them?

950
00:57:28,250 --> 00:57:30,340
一开始很小
So small at first,

951
00:57:30,390 --> 00:57:34,050
然后看他们扩散得多大
then look how they grow.

952
00:57:34,090 --> 00:57:36,820
但是总得有人去开始
But someone has to start them.

953
00:57:36,860 --> 00:57:39,330
他们不会听我们的
They're not going to listen to us.

954
00:57:39,360 --> 00:57:41,660
年轻人 有时候正确的路
Young man, sometimes the right path

955
00:57:41,700 --> 00:57:43,490
往往不是最简单的那条
is not the easiest one.

956
00:57:43,530 --> 00:57:47,530
难道你不明白? 只有当战争停止了...
Don't you see? Only when the fighting stops...

957
00:57:47,570 --> 00:57:50,560
你们才能在一起
can you be together.

958
00:57:53,440 --> 00:57:56,430
好吧 我们去和你父亲谈谈
All right. Let's go talk to your father.

959
00:58:32,610 --> 00:58:34,910
Kocoum! 不!
Kocoum! No!

960
00:58:40,790 --> 00:58:41,980
Kocoum啊!
Kocoum!

961
00:58:46,160 --> 00:58:49,960
放开他!
Leave him alone!

962
00:59:03,850 --> 00:59:05,940
Kocoum! 停下来!
Kocoum! Stop!

963
00:59:08,280 --> 00:59:11,280
双眼睁开
Both eyes open.

964
00:59:18,060 --> 00:59:21,460
- Thomas! - 他...
- Thomas! - Is he...

965
00:59:21,500 --> 00:59:23,360
你杀了他
You killed him.

966
00:59:23,400 --> 00:59:25,370
- 我以为... - 离他远些!
- I thought that... - Get away from him!

967
00:59:25,400 --> 00:59:27,490
Pocahontas 这样没有用的! 他只是...
Pocahontas, it won't help! He was only...

968
00:59:27,540 --> 00:59:28,800
他杀了他!
He killed him!

969
00:59:32,010 --> 00:59:34,640
Thomas 离开这儿!
Thomas, get out of here!

970
00:59:34,680 --> 00:59:37,010
离开这儿!
Get out of here!

971
01:00:39,040 --> 01:00:41,010
谁干的?
Who did this?

972
01:00:41,040 --> 01:00:43,140
Pocahontas在野外树林里
Pocahontas was out in the woods.

973
01:00:43,180 --> 01:00:47,840
Kocoum去找他 这个白人袭击了他
Kocoum went to find her and this white man attacked him.

974
01:00:47,880 --> 01:00:50,280
你们的武器很厉害
Your weapons are strong,

975
01:00:50,320 --> 01:00:53,050
但是现在我的怒火更厉害
but now our anger is stronger.

976
01:00:53,090 --> 01:00:55,890
在太阳升起的时候 首先就将他处死!
At sunrise he will be the first to die!

977
01:00:55,920 --> 01:00:57,080
但是 父亲...
But, Father...

978
01:00:57,130 --> 01:01:00,120
我告诉过你待在部落里
I told you to stay in the village.

979
01:01:00,160 --> 01:01:02,100
你违背了我
You disobeyed me.

980
01:01:02,130 --> 01:01:04,120
你让你的父亲蒙羞!
You have shamed your father!

981
01:01:04,170 --> 01:01:05,960
我只是想做点帮助
I was only trying to help.

982
01:01:06,000 --> 01:01:10,060
就因为你的愚蠢 Kocoum死掉了!
Because of your foolishness, Kocoum is dead!

983
01:01:10,110 --> 01:01:12,370
把他带走!
Take him away!

984
01:01:26,220 --> 01:01:28,950
Kocoum只是想来保护我
Kocoum was just coming to protect me.

985
01:01:28,990 --> 01:01:30,820
Pocahontas啊...
Pocahontas...

986
01:01:30,860 --> 01:01:32,830
是我让Kocoum跟着你的
I sent Kocoum after you.

987
01:01:34,360 --> 01:01:36,890
我很担心你
I was worried about you.

988
01:01:36,930 --> 01:01:39,130
我原以为我做了件正确的事
I-I thought I was doing the right thing.

989
01:01:39,170 --> 01:01:42,600
所有这些都是因我而起
All this happened because of me.

990
01:01:42,640 --> 01:01:47,170
现在我再也见不到John Smith了
And now I'll never see John Smith again.

991
01:01:47,210 --> 01:01:49,010
跟我来
Come with me.

992
01:01:53,620 --> 01:01:55,740
Pocahontas想最后看一眼...
Pocahontas wants to look into the eyes...

993
01:01:55,780 --> 01:01:57,840
那个杀了Kocoum的人
of the man who killed Kocoum.

994
01:02:00,420 --> 01:02:02,150
最好快点
Be quick.

995
01:02:19,710 --> 01:02:22,340
Pocahontas啊
Pocahontas.

996
01:02:24,750 --> 01:02:26,770
我真是抱歉
I'm so sorry.

997
01:02:26,820 --> 01:02:28,280
为了什么? 这件事吗?
For what? This?

998
01:02:28,320 --> 01:02:30,650
比这还糟糕的困境 我都摆脱出来了
I've gotten out of worse scrapes than this.

999
01:02:30,690 --> 01:02:32,620
现在想不起来了 但是...
Can't think of any right now, but...

1000
01:02:32,650 --> 01:02:34,490
如果我们不曾见过 事情也许不会这么糟糕
It would've been better if we'd never met.

1001
01:02:34,520 --> 01:02:36,290
这些事情都不会发生
None of this would've happened.

1002
01:02:36,320 --> 01:02:38,720
Pocahontas 看着我
Pocahontas, look at me.

1003
01:02:38,760 --> 01:02:42,160
我情愿明天就去死...
I'd rather die tomorrow...

1004
01:02:42,200 --> 01:02:44,500
也不要长寿 但不认识你
than live a hundred years without knowing you.

1005
01:02:45,430 --> 01:02:47,170
Pocahontas啊
Pocahontas.

1006
01:02:47,230 --> 01:02:50,170
- 我不能离开你 - 你不会离开我的
- I can't leave you. - You never will.

1007
01:02:50,300 --> 01:02:54,970
不管我发生什么事 我会跟你在一起的 永远
No matter what happens to me, I'll always be with you. Forever.

1008
01:03:08,030 --> 01:03:11,430
救命! 快救命啊! 救命! 救命!
Help! Somebody help! Help! Help!

1009
01:03:11,500 --> 01:03:14,630
- 别急 伙计 怎么了? - Smith! 他们抓住他了!
- Easy, lad. What is it? - It's Smith! They got him!

1010
01:03:14,770 --> 01:03:16,430
- 谁抓住他了? - 野蛮人!
- Who got him? - The savages!

1011
01:03:16,630 --> 01:03:19,100
- 野蛮人? - 他们抓住他了 把他带走了!
- Savages? - They captured him, dragged him off!

1012
01:03:19,170 --> 01:03:20,900
- 他们把他带去哪儿了? - 他们朝北去了
- Where'd they take him? - They headed north.

1013
01:03:20,900 --> 01:03:22,970
- 有多少人? - 我不知道 至少有十来个
- How many were there? - I don't know. At least a dozen.

1014
01:03:23,170 --> 01:03:25,430
- 可恶的畜生! - Ratcliffe是对的!
- Filthy beasts! - Ratcliffe was right!

1015
01:03:25,500 --> 01:03:29,230
太好了 Wiggins 我自己可不能计划的这么好
It's perfect, Wiggins. I couldn't have planned this better myself.

1016
01:03:29,300 --> 01:03:32,370
金子肯定是我的了
The gold is as good as mine.

1017
01:03:32,430 --> 01:03:35,230
我们得救他! 换了我们任何谁 他也会这么做的!
We've got to save him! He'd do the same for any of us!

1018
01:03:35,370 --> 01:03:38,630
- Thomas是对的! 我们得做点什么! - 我们应该做点什么
- Thomas is right! We've got to do somethin'! - And so we shall.

1019
01:03:38,830 --> 01:03:42,500
- 我跟你说过不能信这些野蛮人 - 对!
- I told you those savages couldn't be trusted. - That's right!

1020
01:03:42,700 --> 01:03:45,830
Smith想跟他们成为朋友 看看他们对他做了什么!
Smith tried to befriend them, and look what they've done to him!

1021
01:03:45,830 --> 01:03:49,970
- 嗯 对 - 而现在我宣布是时候去救我们勇敢的同志了
- Yeah, that's right. - But now I say it's time to rescue our courageous comrade.

1022
01:03:50,030 --> 01:03:53,630
天一亮 我们就进攻!
At daybreak, we attack!

1023
01:03:53,700 --> 01:03:57,030
对这些无赖我们还能期待什么呢
What can you expect from filthy little heathens

1024
01:03:57,100 --> 01:04:00,230
- 当有不同种族的时候就会发生这种事 - 没错
- Here's what you get when races are diverse - That's right.

1025
