1033
01:04:33,030 --> 01:04:36,570
# 这是一场我们害怕的战争 那些白脸的都是魔鬼 #
# This is what we feared The pale face is a demon #

1034
01:04:36,630 --> 01:04:39,770
# 他们仅有的感觉是贪婪 #
# The only thing they feel at all is greed #

1035
01:04:39,830 --> 01:04:43,300
# 在那乳白色的皮肤之下 里面全都是空的 #
# Beneath that milky hide there's empatiness inside #

1036
01:04:43,500 --> 01:04:46,100
# 我怀疑他们会不会流血 #
# I wonder if they even bleed #

1037
01:04:46,170 --> 01:04:50,230
# - 他们是野蛮人 野蛮人 - 几乎不是人类 #
# - They're savages, savages - Barely even human #

1038
01:04:50,300 --> 01:04:53,370
# - 野蛮人 野蛮人 - 本质上是凶手 #
# - Savages, savages - Killers at the core #

1039
01:04:53,430 --> 01:04:57,170
# 他们和我们不一样 他们不能被信任 #
# They're different from us which means they can't be trusted #

1040
01:04:57,230 --> 01:05:00,230
# 我们要敲响战鼓 #
# We must sound the drums of war #

1041
01:05:00,300 --> 01:05:04,030
# - 他们是野蛮人 野蛮人 - 首先让我们来处理这个 #
# - They're savages, savages - First we deal with this one #

1042
01:05:04,100 --> 01:05:07,230
# - 然后我们敲响战鼓 - 野蛮人 野蛮人 #
# - Then we sound the drums of war - Savages, savages #

1043
01:05:07,430 --> 01:05:09,030
# 让我们去杀掉几个 伙计们! #
# Let's go get a few, men! #

1044
01:05:09,170 --> 01:05:12,570
# - 野蛮人 野蛮人 - 现在就靠你们了 各位 #
# - Savages, savages - Now it's up to you, men #

1045
01:05:12,700 --> 01:05:14,430
# - 野蛮人 - 野蛮人 #
# - Savages - Savages #

1046
01:05:14,500 --> 01:05:16,170
# 几乎不是人类 #
# Barely even human #

1047
01:05:16,300 --> 01:05:19,700
# 现在我们敲响 #
# Now we sound the drums #

1048
01:05:19,770 --> 01:05:21,230
# 战 #
# Of #

1049
01:05:21,370 --> 01:05:28,100
# 鼓 #
# War #

1050
01:05:31,630 --> 01:05:36,030
- 他们准备在太阳升起的时候处决他 Willow奶奶 - 你得去制止他们
- They're going to kill him at sunrise, Grandmother Willow. - You have to stop them.

1051
01:05:36,100 --> 01:05:39,630
- 我没有办法 - 孩子 记住你那个梦
- I can't. - Child, remember your dream.

1052
01:05:39,770 --> 01:05:43,570
我错了 Willow奶奶 我走错了一条路
I was wrong, Grandmother Willow. I followed the wrong path.

1053
01:05:43,700 --> 01:05:46,030
我感到很失落
I feel so lost.

1054
01:06:03,300 --> 01:06:05,570
指南针?
The compass?

1055
01:06:13,230 --> 01:06:15,300
旋转的指针
Spinning arrow.

1056
01:06:15,300 --> 01:06:17,500
这是你梦里的指针
It's the arrow from your dream.

1057
01:06:17,630 --> 01:06:20,970
我是对的! 它正指向他
I was right! It was pointing to him.

1058
01:06:27,500 --> 01:06:30,100
- 日出 - 还不晚 孩子
- Sunrise. - It's not too late, child.

1059
01:06:30,300 --> 01:06:34,230
让大地的灵魂来指引你
Let the spirits of the Earth guide you.

1060
01:06:35,370 --> 01:06:37,830
你知道你的路 孩子
You know your path, child.

